<enN0003>Morimoto

///================================================================================

//TEXT
<jaT0001>Then, as they began walking...
<enT0001>Then, as they began walking...

//TEXT 【Long-haired Girl】
<jaT0002>"Umm, excuse me?"
<enT0002>"Umm, excuse me?"

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0003>"Hmm, me?"
<enT0003>"Hmm, me?"

//TEXT 【Long-haired Girl】
<jaT0004>"Yes, Umm, I'm looking for a friend of mine, a girl about this tall, with short hair. Have you seen her?"
<enT0004>"Yes, Umm, I'm looking for a friend of mine, a girl about this tall, with short hair. Have you seen her?"

//TEXT
<jaT0005>She said and held her hand at about her forehead to show the height of her friend.
<enT0005>She said and held her hand at about her forehead to show the height of her friend.

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0006>"No, I haven't seen her."
<enT0006>"No, I haven't seen her."

//TEXT
<jaT0007>She asked Morimoto with a glance, but he shook his head in silence. He hadn't seen her either.
<enT0007>She asked Morimoto with a glance, but he shook his head in silence. He hadn't seen her either.

//TEXT 【Long-haired Girl】
<jaT0008>"I see... Then if you'll excuse me."
<enT0008>"I see... Then if you'll excuse me."

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0009>"Uh-huh."
<enT0009>"Uh-huh."

//TEXT
<jaT0010>......
<enT0010>......

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0011>"Now then, us too."
<enT0011>"Now then, us too."

//TEXT
<jaT0012>As he started to walk, he turned back towards Morimoto. It was then that Shuhei finally noticed something odd about him.
<enT0012>As he started to walk, he turned back towards Morimoto. It was then that Shuhei finally noticed something odd about him.

//TEXT 【Morimoto】
<jaT0013>"......"
<enT0013>"......"

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0014>"Hmm? What's wrong, you're staring after that girl that left. Something bothering you?"
<enT0014>"Hmm? What's wrong, you're staring after that girl that left. Something bothering you?"

//TEXT 【Morimoto】
<jaT0015>"Huh?"
<enT0015>"Huh?"

//TEXT 【Morimoto】
<jaT0016>"Oh, it is nothing, really. You gave her an amorous look, so I thought, 'Hmm? So this is the type of girl Shuhei-san goes for?' and watched her for a bit."
<enT0016>"Oh, it is nothing, really. You gave her an amorous look, so I thought, 'Hmm? So this is the type of girl Shuhei-san goes for?' and watched her for a bit."

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0017>"Wha?! I did no such thing! I simply answered her question like a normal person!"
<enT0017>"Wha?! I did no such thing! I simply answered her question like a normal person!"

//TEXT 【Morimoto】
<jaT0018>"My dear guest, you have exquisite taste. That girl is quite something. Heh heh heh"
<enT0018>"My dear guest, you have exquisite taste. That girl is quite something. Heh heh heh"

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0019>"Why do you sound like the manager of a sex shop recommending his poster girl..."
<enT0019>"Why do you sound like the manager of a sex shop recommending his poster girl..."

//TEXT 【Morimoto】
<jaT0020>"Just a joke. Now, let us head for your room quickly. We should not merely stand here talking like this."
<enT0020>"Just a joke. Now, let us head for your room quickly. We should not merely stand here talking like this."

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0021>"Right, right."
<enT0021>"Right, right."

//TEXT
<jaT0022>Shuhei nodded, looking worn out.
<enT0022>Shuhei nodded, looking worn out.

